OL,3,CPolice Ombudsman steps down over
OL,4,C'commentary'
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland's Police Ombudsman
OL,7,Fhas announced she is taking a
OL,8,Ftemporary leave of absence with
OL,9,Fimmediate effect.
OL,11,FMarie Anderson had planned to retire
OL,12,Fin December but said she had taken a
OL,13,Fdecision to take a temporary leave due
OL,14,Fto "current commentary" that is
OL,15,F"detracting from the focus" of her
OL,16,Fwork with bereaved families.
