OL,3,CPolice Ombudsman steps down over
OL,4,C'commentary'
OL,6,FIt comes following the conclusion of
OL,7,Fan independent investigation into an
OL,8,Falleged domestic incident at Ms
OL,9,FAnderson's home in September 2023,
OL,10,Fwith a file of evidence sent to the
OL,11,FPublic Prosecution Service (PPS).
OL,13,FMs Anderson has not appeared in public
OL,14,Fsince September 2023.
OL,16,FA man was arrested as part of the
OL,17,Finquiry and later released pending a
OL,18,Freport to prosecutors.
