OL,6,FA file was subsequently sent to the
OL,7,FPublic Prosecution Service (PPS) and a
OL,8,Fcaution issued to the man who had been
OL,9,Farrested.
OL,11,FThe investigation was carried out by
OL,12,FWest Midlands Police at the request of
OL,13,Fthe PSNI.
OL,15,FFollowing the incident Marie Anderson
OL,16,Freturned to work in January this year.
OL,17,FThere have been growing calls for her
OL,18,Fto step aside.
