OL,3,CPolice Ombudsman steps down over
OL,4,C'commentary'
OL,6,FThe legislation is built in such a way
OL,7,Fas to mean she can not be compelled to
OL,8,Fstand aside.
OL,10,FOn Tuesday, Ms Anderson announced her
OL,11,Fdeparture.
OL,13,FShe said she has delegated authority
OL,14,Fto her office's chief executive and
OL,15,Fsenior staff to ensure the work of the
OL,16,Foffice continues in her absence.
