OL,3,CPolice Ombudsman steps down over
OL,4,C'commentary'
OL,6,FMs Anderson said: "Although I had
OL,7,Fdecided to retire in December this
OL,8,Fyear, which would have allowed me to
OL,9,Ffulfil my commitments to delivering
OL,10,Fthe outcomes of investigations to a
OL,11,Fnumber of bereaved families, it has
OL,12,Fbecome increasingly clear that current
OL,13,Fcommentary is detracting from the
OL,14,Ffocus of that work.
OL,16,F"I am extremely grateful to those
OL,17,Ffamilies who put their trust in me and
OL,18,Fit is their interests which are at the
OL,19,Fheart of my decision today to take a
OL,20,Ftemporary leave of absence with
OL,21,Fimmediate effect.
